      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nI do have one concern.  The reason I did the spec.in that way was to handle once upstream client is out of staging. In the case lnet/lustre uapi will show up in /usr/include/linux/xxx. This could result in the case where users build against the wrong headers. Well I guess we can handle that case when it comes up.",
